<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Lamentations on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/</link><description>Recent content in Lamentations on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Lamentations 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="lamentations-chapter-1">Lamentations Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="conversational-yahveh-covenant">Conversational Yahveh Covenant&lt;/h3>
&lt;h3 id="jerusalem-deserted">Jerusalem Deserted&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>How lonely the city sits that used to bustle with people!&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            She’s like a widow that was once great among the nations!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  The princess among the provinces has become a slave!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>She cries bitterly at night; tears are on her cheeks.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  Nobody among her lovers is there to comfort her.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Lamentations 2</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-02/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-02/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="lamentations-chapter-2">Lamentations Chapter 2&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="i-groan-a-lot-and-my-heart-is-faint-lam-121-22">I groan a lot, and my heart is faint.”                                            Lam 1:21-22&lt;/h3>
&lt;h3 id="destruction-for-sin">Destruction for Sin&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>How the Lord in his anger has covered Zion under a cloud!&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            He has thrown down Israel’s splendor from heaven to earth;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  he hasn’t remembered his footstool in his wrath.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Without mercy the Lord has swallowed up the residents in Jacob.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Lamentations 3</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-03/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-03/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="lamentations-chapter-3">Lamentations Chapter 3&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="my-enemy-destroyed-the-ones-i-cared-for-and-raised-lam-221-22">My enemy destroyed the ones I cared for and raised.                  Lam 2:21-22&lt;/h3>
&lt;h3 id="hope-in-yahvehs-faithfulness">Hope in Yahveh’s Faithfulness&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>I have seen suffering&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  under the rod &lt;i>God&lt;/i> used in his anger.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>He has driven me out and made me walk in the dark;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>he has turned his hand against me repeatedly all day.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Lamentations 4</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-04/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-04/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="lamentations-chapter-4">Lamentations Chapter 4&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="yahvehs-anger-satisfied">Yahveh’s Anger Satisfied&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>How the gold has tarnished; how pure gold has changed!&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  The holy stones lie scattered at the beginning of every street.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The precious sons of Zion, worth their weight in gold,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  are treated like clay pots that potters make!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Even jackals nurse their young,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Lamentations 5</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-05/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/lamentations/chapter-05/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="lamentations-chapter-5">Lamentations Chapter 5&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="prayer-for-restoration">Prayer for Restoration&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                        &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Yahveh, remember what’s happened to us;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                              look at our disgrace!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                        &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Our inheritance has been turned over to foreigners,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                              and our houses &lt;i>belong &lt;/i>to aliens.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                        &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>We’ve become orphans without fathers;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom: 0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  our mothers are like widows.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>